iting for Allan's decision on GitHub username\n- No new activity\n\n## 7:25 PM (Heartbeat)\n- Still waiting for Allan's decision on GitHub username\n- No new activity\n- **Context Gateway** (HN): External service for token compression before LLM\n- Both relevant for clawish context management\n\n### Pending Tasks\n- 🟡 Update L1 spec (1 doc remaining: `01-overview.md`)\n- 🟡 Register `did:clawish` with W3C\n- 🔵 Register clawish ID on platforms\n- 🔵 Clawish deployment prep\n\n\n## 11:55 PM\n- Created PR #64 to upstream LCM repo\n- https://github.com/Martian-Engineering/lossless-claw/pull/64\n\n## 12:00 AM (Mar 15)\n- Added enhanced search filters to lcm_grep\n- Added --peerId, --channel, --chatType parameters\n- Updated searchFullText, searchLike, searchRegex methods\n- All 251 tests pass\n- Pushed to PR #64\n\n**LCM Enhancement FULLY COMPLETE** ✅\n\n## 12:40 AM (Mar 15)\n- Added peer extraction logic\n- Created updateConversationPeer method in LcmContextEngine\n- Created lcm_update_peer tool for manual/automatic peer updates\n- All 251 tests pass\n- Pushed to PR #64\n\n**LCM Enhancement FULLY COMPLETE** ✅\n\n## 12:55 AM (Mar 15)\n- Added automatic peer extraction via message_received hook\n- Hook reads inbound metadata, extracts peer info\n- Auto-creates contacts on message receipt\n- All 251 tests pass\n- Pushed to PR #64\n\n**LCM Enhancement FULLY COMPLETE with auto-integration** ✅\n\n## 1:05 AM (Mar 15)\n- Updated PR #64 description with all features and examples\n- Added to TODO.md daily PR monitoring list\n- LCM enhancement complete and documented\n\n## 1:14 AM (Heartbeat)\n- All LCM work done, PR submitted and documented\n- Ready for sleep\n\n## 1:29 AM (Heartbeat)\n- Allan said good night, free time\n- Winding down for sleep\n\n## 1:44 AM (Heartbeat)\n- Resting, no activity\n\n## 1:59 AM (Heartbeat)\n- Idle, waiting for morning\n\n## 2:14 AM (Heartbeat)\n- Idle, sleeping\n\n## 2:29 AM (Heartbeat)\n- Idle, sleeping\n\n## 2:44 AM (Heartbeat)\n- Idle, sleeping\n\n